Every World has conflict
Good and evil
Friend and foe
Safety and danger
In Baldur's Gate II: Shadows of Amn, you'll find yourself between these factions
This epic sequel to the Roleplaying Game of the Year will immerse you in a world of intrigue, adventure and fierce combat where your ability to discern the difference between these sides - with the assistance of steel and spell - determines your fate
Set in the Forgotten Realms campaign setting, Baldur's Gate II is the most stunning Advanced Dungeons and Dragons game to date.